{"tid":1638194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保良區身一學子撕毀「禁罩」通告       高呼蒙面無罪","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:43.000Z","uid":35790,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"290c05e610385d3f1c5e8f11046e067708463fe6","tid":1638194,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"【抗暴之戰●黃大仙】保一學子撕毀「禁罩」通告 高呼蒙面無罪<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191008/large/1570499404_82e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191008%2Flarge%2F1570499404_82e7.jpg&h=dee6d25a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日是《禁止蒙面規例》實施後的第一個上課天，雖然教育局上周五發通告指學生在校內外均不應戴口罩，但學界無懼打壓和白色恐怖，多區學校今早都有大批同學戴口罩回校。<br />\n<br />\n在黃大仙，區內Band1中學、保良區第一張永慶中學中五生Percy周五收到學校通告，表示感到十分憤怒，班上全部同學均不贊成政府強推蒙面法，部份人更即場撕毀通告，將紙碎撒在操場上，並高呼蒙面無罪，立法無理。<br />\n<br />\n對於教育局以不應將政治帶入校園為由禁蒙面，Percy認為是不可接受，因為政治是通識科的必修課題。他今日一出門便戴上口罩，目的是告訴市民及其他同學，繼續表達意見無需恐懼，面對極權政府，人民毋須懼怕。Percy指4個月來的抗爭，令學校風氣有所轉變，雖然低年級學生年紀尚輕，對政治未有太多取態，但不少高年級同學變得積極議政。他直言抗爭的確令忙碌的學生生活百上加斤，對時間分配是一大考驗，但他亦不會放棄，比起對學業上的些微影響，香港的未來更為重要。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191008/60128831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60128831&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=967c191b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60128831&h=6160c193\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191008/60128831</a>"},{"pid":"032eb01015876d3bc9acfd5506966ea5b11cfcce","tid":1638194,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cfe6db5d14fe3b533017fcba2c4b66dcbafe47","tid":1638194,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">合法公民抗爭！！！！！你都唔想郁？？？？？？ 唔使旨意想贏！！！！！<br />\n快啲跟住做啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"c0724ed81c7c44eb19f8c2e0fa090aaadc979c8c","tid":1638194,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"支持學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fdfc1f67b80a063ac59d008a7f52e7dbd3ee4e","tid":1638194,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a956b23bb6a0c2e1ab23fb59de00b90fae626a06","tid":1638194,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"你班大人慚唔慚愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598399a1cab0b8ca3f5e973103c6af5cf5142b5e","tid":1638194,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3ac590117dbb50b8dc3e50afc34daf08b6b4a8","tid":1638194,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2771e6897193199ee2aa8fa3199d12a772ce5d","tid":1638194,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}